title: S8E03 – "Strange Tastes" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you four spine-chilling tales from author Ryan Peacock, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about freakish farms, ‘death’ metal, creepy cuisines, and merciless mentalists.
